 all have to put up with it. We have all heard or been involved in people trying to get flags when not a part of raid. What is the solution, if any? <br>
<br>
No clue. Lets face it, it's a game. Unless you are part of a hardcore guild, you will probably never see the elemental planes unless VI changes things. Yeah, all of you are holding your breath for that to happen right? <br>
<br>
Another reason for this post, to vent. OMG you think. Oh well, some time has passed and ya know, why does one guild hate another guild? Why do players hate other players? Some players have done naughty things to others, so have guilds, but where do we draw the line? When does it stop?<br>
<br>
Recently a guild killed Behemoth. Sure, you know who you are, but I'm not gonna name names cause it's not important really. NE offered to help, lets face it, we wanted to help to kill the mob plus get flagged. No deep dark secret there. Our offer was rejected. We waited. Mob dead, we left. Well, ok, maybe a few attempted to hail the gnome, but humans will be humans.<br>
<br>
Within hours rants and flames appeared on the ol' karana flame boards. No biggie really. Ever played that game where you line a bunch of people up and start at one end with a sentence or two and see what it ends up being at the end? Yeah.. people view everything, read everything from their own perspective and it's influenced by their own beliefs. <br>
<br>
Anyhows, back to my rant. Yesterday. 2 guilds going for same mob. Suddenly I start getting tells asking if player x, y, and z can come help. I'm really not a mean person, heck, in real life I'm a nurse, ya know, one of those angels of mercy! But I wasn't really running this raid, I was just kinda going along and making sure my guys knew what was going on and what to do. I had a bizillion tells and couldn't even keep up with trying to get my own guild members tells. If I missed yours, I wasn't ignoring you. Well, not intentionally <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
Mob dead. Suddenly every Tom, Dick, Harriet from every guild across Karana appeared in zone. Total chaos. Darn zone was lagged out the Behemoth's rather dead metal posterior and the poor gnome was being bombarded with hails. <br>
<br>
Never have I seen such an onslaught of people for a flag. People training other people, dead people, people hailing, tells that lagged me to almost a complete stop. Yeah, there for a bit I was rather.. pissed. I admit it, I cheered when I heard a train killed the gnome.<br>
<br>
Honestly, and I can only speak for myself, it's nice to have the flag to get into tactics, but it didn't mean much. Ya know that feeling when your guild alone killed that big mob and you were like, &quot;wow!&quot; I didn't feel that. In a way it's a let down. Sure, a lot of my guild is there, but a lot isn't. I want to kill it again with just my peeps. <br>
<br>
The game isn't about who is first to me. It isn't about who has what gear, who is better or this or that. I want to know that my guild killed said mob alone. I want that lil bit of &quot;hell yes!&quot; feeling. <br>
<br>
At first I was a lil pissed about the flag thing. Now, I'm not. It will be interesting to see if any of these other guilds will let my guild members who missed the flag hail their mob. If they don't, that's ok by me. I can't wait for the opportunity to kill this big mess of tin cans alone, just my guild. That's all I want. Just the satisfaction of being left alone, letting us do our own thing. Heck, I'm willing to bet a few of you other guilds might feel the same, maybe not though. <br>
<br>
A lot has been posted, whispered, and flamed about Night Eternal. We aren't so bad really. <br>
<br>
Anyhows, grats to all those that got flags. The system sucks. Once a majority of the guild is flagged, it's a shame that others can't get the flag or at least get into the zone on a raid situation. Total stupidity really. Time sinks, gotta love em. <br>
<br>
If this turns into a flame fest of one guild against another, I will delete or lock this thread, but honestly, it would be nice to maybe hear other rants, erm I mean opinions on this. <br>
<br>
